ted meats, or as an impressive vegetarian main.","While any combination of root vegetables will work well in this dish, using beetroot gives the gratin a wonderful ruby colour.","Slicing all the vegetables the same thickness helps to ensure they cook at the same time."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","6 portions"]}